title: Neal Brennan Interview
itunes:title: Neal Brennan Interview
description:
Today on the show we had our guy comedian/writer Neal Brennan stop by where he spoke about Ayahuasca Revelations, PC Culture, New Comedy Special and more. Also, they had jamaican artist Noah Powa who spoke about relationships, Jamaican Culture, Angela Yee Day and more. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to another Floridian, with this time being a doctor who was removed for offering $50 mask opt-out letters.
